                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">This colorful, magical and mind-expanding volume is an encyclopedia that only the people at Ripley's Believe It or Not!(r)could dream up. Every page is brimming with information and eye-popping artwork, covering the extremes of every subject imaginable. Coincidences, explorers, human anatomy, laws, medicine, science, sports, survival, villains, war, weather-these are just a few of the topics explored in this unique volume. </span>
              
</td></tr></table>
